title: Ep. 129 - Why You Should Not Be Concerned with Europe
itunes:title: Why You Should Not Be Concerned with Europe
description: Andrew Horowitz, host of The Disciplined Investor podcast, sees more bailouts ahead for Europe. He also breaks down earnings season and gives us his three favorite ideas with huge short-term upside potential.
